					href="../register">Register</a></li>
				<li sec:authorize="isAuthenticated()" class="nav-item mx-4">Welcome
					<span sec:authentication="principal.username">User</span>
				</li>
				<li sec:authorize="isAuthenticated()" class="nav-item mx-4"><a
